---
title: Honey-Glazed Pork Tenderloin with Roasted Potatoes and Broccoli
description: A honey glaze may sound like something that goes with dessert, but mild-tasting pork loves a sweet sauce too, especially one that has a few savory elements in it for contrast. In this recipe, you’ll be folding an extra-large drizzle of honey into a rich, savory pan sauce, then spooning it onto pork tenderloin (and the roasted sweet potatoes and green beans, if you like).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-glazed-pork-tenderloin-ad566fe2.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/honey-glazed-pork-tenderloin-5d2ca6b50ef749001177bb97-ce3ac7c2.pdf
nutrition:
